{"tid":1972937,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬道立對捍衞法院之戰感沮喪","createTime":"2020-04-15T00:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T01:14:44.000Z","uid":103981,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b75302607d620cbde656e3affb1ba78fa0fe15e9","tid":1972937,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T00:18:36.000Z","msg":"有接近馬道立的人說，雖然他不是被迫離開，但持續的捍衞法院之戰已令他日漸沮喪（the constant battle to safeguard the judiciary has worn on him），其工作包括處理訪港的內地法官及中央駐港官員給予的「訓話」（His job includes dealing with visiting mainland judges and briefings from locally based Chinese officials），這些工作可以是很棘手。<br />\n<br />\n他們又說，中國法官及官員定期向馬道立宣傳北京的愛國議程，強調司法機構捍衞中國主權和國家安全的重要性。一名認識馬道立的人說，馬面對不理解香港三權分立、司法獨立真正價值的黨政官僚時，已感到疲累。（I know he tires of the apparatchiks whose Communist Party mantra has no room for even starting to grasp the separation of powers that exists in Hong Kong, or the real meaning or value of judicial independence）。有時馬道立甚至停止再說相關議題，改為嘗試討論足球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/Lxq_vJGuA5YVfY63Ze0j9mpqIc8=/375x375/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/VKG4TCMF3D5TLJ4D46TE5KIPFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FLxq_vJGuA5YVfY63Ze0j9mpqIc8%3D%2F375x375%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FVKG4TCMF3D5TLJ4D46TE5KIPFI.jpg&h=1bac550f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200414/GGZGOGVPFJOSIHGIF2KVTJC36I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200414%2FGGZGOGVPFJOSIHGIF2KVTJC36I%2F&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWbTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=a072a46b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200414%2FGGZGOGVPFJOSIHGIF2KVTJC36I%2F&h=3ce5f342\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200414/GGZGOGVPFJOSIHGIF2KVTJC36I/</a>"},{"pid"